                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">Police Sergeant S</hi> 8). I was formerly 746 A—I was a witness against the prisoner when he was convicted in 1867—I am positive he is the man.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18730922-name-129" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18730922-name-129" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18730922-name-129" type="surname" value="SMITH"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18730922-name-129" type="given" value="SIDNEY ROBERTS"></interp>SIDNEY ROBERTS SMITH</persName>
                  </hi>. I am clerk to the gaol of Newgate—I know the prisoner as McShay—he was undergoing a sentence of
seven years' penal servitude for uttering counterfeit coin.</p>
